        <scopecontent>
            <p>This collection consists chiefly of correspondence, photographs, negatives, slides, contact sheets, clippings, articles (including two longer book-length ones), guidelines for restoration, and related materials that were compiled during the restoration of the Butler Mansion on Delaware Avenue and North Steet in the 1980s. The collection also contains two folders of clippings on the Metcalfe House.</p>
        </scopecontent>
